OL,4,G0100FOutback Truckers
OL,5,     GIt's mid-afternoon in Perth and
OL,6,     GDion's super size convoy is
OL,7,     Gpushing hard to get out of the
OL,8,     Gcity before sunset. And the fate
OL,9,     Gof Steve's trip hangs on one
OL,10,     Gphone call to his mechanic.
OL,11,G0200FTrucking Hell
OL,12,     GNear Durham, Alpha Recovery
OL,13,     Gconfronts a rare challenge: a
OL,14,     Gdouble-decker bus on its side.
OL,15,G0300FTrucking Hell
OL,16,     GA tipper truck sinks into deep
OL,17,     Gmud on an isolated farm track, a
OL,18,     Gcar has crashed onto an
OL,19,     Gembankment, and a lorry breaks
OL,20,     Gdown off a busy roundabout in
OL,21,     Grush hour.
